-08-16T20:31:23.000Z","msg":"樓主講嘅嘢<br />\n之前有人做過研究<br />\n<br />\n<em>Keyword censorship is no longer transparent. In the past, users received notification when their message was blocked; now censorship of chat messages happens without any user notice.</em><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://citizenlab.ca/2016/11/wechat-china-censorship-one-app-two-systems/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcitizenlab.ca%2F2016%2F11%2Fwechat-china-censorship-one-app-two-systems%2F&d=u3dPEc69Okhs1BcqxCk75edgoykoOisTuuABwIAScok%3D&h=1d1a90cc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://citizenlab.ca/2016/11/wechat-china-censorship-one-app-two-systems/</a><br />\n<br />\n<em>關鍵詞審查不再透明。過去，如果某條信息被過濾，微信用戶會收到提示，但現在審查變為悄然進行。</em><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://citizenlab.ca/2016/12/一app两制：微信如何区别审查中国及海外用户/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcitizenlab.ca%2F2016%2F12%2F%E4%B8%80app%E4%B8%A4%E5%88%B6%EF%BC%9A%E5%BE%AE%E4%BF%A1%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E5%8C%BA%E5%88%AB%E5%AE%A1%E6%9F%A5%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E5%8F%8A%E6%B5%B7%E5%A4%96%E7%94%A8%E6%88%B7%2F&d=u3dPEc69Okhs1BcqxCk75edgoykoOisTuuABwIAScok%3D&h=0a7b1ba5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://citizenlab.ca/2016/12/一app两制：微信如何区别审查中国及海外用户/</a>"},{"pid":"1d22a1a745292841c6070456bc9441a73721e9a4","tid":1479182,"uid":143481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7c8d4091c0d49353c83ac8250510a56c2246fa73","tid":1479182,"uid":264780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T20:31:23.000Z","msg":"樓主講嘅嘢<br />\n之前有人做過研究<br />\n<br />\n<em>Keyword censorship is no longer transparent. In the past, users received notification when their message was blocked; now censorship of chat messages happens without any user notice.</em><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://citizenlab.ca/2016/11/wechat-china-censorship-one-app-two-systems/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcitizenlab.ca%2F2016%2F11%2Fwechat-china-censorship-one-app-two-systems%2F&d=u3dPEc69Okhs1BcqxCk75edg